    Create a collection links section with three collection cards in a responsive grid layout. Include heading "Shop our collections". Each card should have: luxury handbags, premium bags, and artisan accessories with their respective descriptions and "Explore Collection â†’" buttons. Style with dark minimalist theme, full-width images with transparent overlays, white outline buttons that invert on hover, Helvetica Neue font with bold titles. Add hover zoom animation for images and scroll-reveal fade-in slide-up effects for cards. Responsive design: one row on desktop, stacked on mobile., should be horizotal ina 3x grid then below a button to all collection

